modName: Geralts Leather jacket from The Witcher2
summary: This mod puts Geralts Leather Jackt from The Witcher2 into ypur game.
descriptionHtml:
This MOD adds just Geralt\'s light leather Jacket of CDProject\'s The Witcher2.
This armor is not currently craftable and only by the consolen code to get.
Boots, gloves, and other stuff you can download AlphaWolff\'s ultimate Witcher mod L0rd0fwar\'s the Witcher2 Modells mod, TH3WICK3D1\'s Blue Stripes Commando mod
and H4lfD3ad Better Shrouded Armor mod.

Witcher ultimate mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9198

The Witcher2 model: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5588

Blue Stripes Commando: Vernon Roche-Ves: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7807

Better Shrouded Armor: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12015

To find the console code write /help jacket and you have got the code.
author: TheWitcher5688
